OL,3,CAI helping to cut waiting times in A&E
OL,4,Cthis winter
OL,6,FHospitals in England are using
OL,7,Fartificial intelligence (AI) to help
OL,8,Fcut waiting times in emergency
OL,9,Fdepartments this winter, officials
OL,10,Fhave said.
OL,12,FThe AI tool, which was launched in
OL,13,F2024, provides hospitals in England
OL,14,Fwith anticipated A&E admissions three
OL,15,Fweeks in advance and alerts them to
OL,16,Fpotential upcoming surges, allowing
OL,17,Ftrusts to better plan for shifts and
OL,18,Fbed space.
