OL,6,FThe technology allows healthcare staff
OL,7,F"to do the things that they're trained
OL,8,Fto do, rather than having to be bound
OL,9,Fdown by bureaucratic processes,"
OL,10,Faccording to officials.
OL,12,FIan Murray, minister for digital
OL,13,Fgovernment and data, told the Press
OL,14,FAssociation: "The front door of the
OL,15,FNHS is the A&E department.
