OL,3,CAI helping to cut waiting times in A&E
OL,4,Cthis winter
OL,6,F"You've no idea how many people will
OL,7,Fcome through the door, although you
OL,8,Fcan have some analytical evidence that
OL,9,FSaturday nights might be busier than a
OL,10,FTuesday night, for example, and the
OL,11,Fwinter might be busier than the
OL,12,Fsummer, unless you have a heatwave, of
OL,13,Fcourse.
OL,15,F"It helps us to predict how busy their
OL,16,FA&E departments are going to be.
OL,18,F"If you put that into context and see
OL,19,Fseasonal trends, along with how busy
OL,20,Fdays are going to be, you can then put
OL,21,Fyour resources in the right place.
