OL,6,F"So you can have more consultants of a
OL,7,Fparticular variety on. You can have
OL,8,Fmore nursing staff on.
OL,10,F"You can maybe then see about freeing
OL,11,Fup beds further down the pipeline,
OL,12,Fmaybe see how you might need to get
OL,13,Fmore people out of the hospital
OL,14,Fquicker, and free up those beds."
