OL,4,Cthis winter
OL,6,FThe A&E Admissions Forecasting Tool is
OL,7,Ftrained on historic data, including
OL,8,Fweather trends, to determine how many
OL,9,Fpeople are likely to visit A&E.
OL,11,FAround 50 NHS organisations are
OL,12,Falready using the tool, and according
OL,13,Fto Murray they are "seeing great
OL,14,Fresults".
OL,16,FHe added: "It's about concentrating
OL,17,Fwhat the NHS needs.
