OL,3,CAI helping to cut waiting times in A&E
OL,4,Cthis winter
OL,6,F"It's about modernising the NHS, using
OL,7,Fthe tools to allow clinicians and
OL,8,Fprofessionals to do the things that
OL,9,Fthey're trained to do, rather than
OL,10,Fhaving to be bound down by
OL,11,Fbureaucratic processes, allowing
OL,12,Fresources to be targeted where they
OL,13,Fneed to be targeted."
OL,15,FThe tool forms part of Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer's AI Exemplars programme. In
OL,17,FJanuary, the Prime Minister said AI
OL,18,Fwill "drive incredible change in our
OL,19,Fcountry".
