OL,4,Cthis winter
OL,6,FTechnology Secretary Liz Kendall said:
OL,7,F"AI is already improving healthcare by
OL,8,Fspeeding up diagnosis and unlocking
OL,9,Fnew treatments. Now we are going a
OL,10,Fstep further.
OL,12,F"By helping to predict demand, this AI
OL,13,Fforecasting tool is getting patients
OL,14,Fthe care they need faster while
OL,15,Fsupporting our incredible NHS staff.
OL,17,F"That means easing pressure by
OL,18,Fensuring the NHS is at the forefront
OL,19,Fof the latest technology during the
OL,20,Fbusiest time of year."
