OL,6,FProfessor Julian Redhead, national
OL,7,Fmedical director for urgent and
OL,8,Femergency care at NHS England, said:
OL,9,F"Early and efficient planning is key
OL,10,Fto managing busy periods like winter,
OL,11,Fand new tech like the AI tool has the
OL,12,Fpotential to make a real difference to
OL,13,Fthe way we manage care for patients."
